---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Choosing the Best Return Management Software for eCommerce - parcelLab"
  description="Discover how the right return management software can streamline your ecommerce operations, reduce return rates, and improve customer satisfaction."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Returns</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Choosing the Best Return Management Software for eCommerce</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Tobias Buxhoidt</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2023-05-06">May 6, 2023</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>7 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Return management software (RMS) is a tool that facilitates the returns process, from initiating a return to issuing refunds. It helps businesses manage returns efficiently, saving time and costs while improving customer satisfaction.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Features to Look For</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">1. Full Integration</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Your RMS must seamlessly connect with ecommerce platforms, order management systems, and shipping carriers. Look for headless providers that integrate with your existing workflow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">2. White-Labeled Communications</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Find software that's 100% white-labeled -- all post-purchase communications should look like they come directly from your brand, not the vendor.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">3. Flexible Rules and Multi-Channel Support</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Partner with a solution that provides granular options and flexible rules for customized returns experiences, with omnichannel support across all selling platforms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">4. Data-Driven Insights</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">You need an enterprise returns solution that provides actionable insights to reduce your returns rate and improve your top-line revenue.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">5. Reliable Customer Support</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Find a provider with quick response times, availability across multiple time zones, and detailed self-service resources.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab handles the post-purchase experience across 175 countries for over 700 brands, tracking over 350 shipping carriers with 100% white-labeled, on-brand communications.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
